WEBVTT FILE

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to RustChain, a high-performance blockchain built with Rust for maximum safety and efficiency.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
RustChain leverages Rust's memory safety without garbage collection to create a secure, fast blockchain platform.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Our unique consensus mechanism combines proof-of-stake with innovative verification techniques.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Key features include atomic cross-chain transactions, WASM smart contract support, and modular architecture.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:55.000
RustChain provides developers with a robust environment for building decentralized applications.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Join the RustChain ecosystem today. Visit our GitHub for documentation and start building.